headline: Apple interested in using AI to design custom chips- Reuters, citing exec
summary: Investing.com-- Apple Inc (NASDAQ:AAPL) is interested in using generative artificial intelligence to help design its custom chips, Reuters reported on Wednesday, citing recent comments from a top executive in the technology giant.
